(1166, '내일 저녁에 만날 수 있어요?', 'Tomorrow evening can you meet up?', 'phrase', '1B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.1 SNU.lvl.1B SNU.lvl.1B.ch16'),
(1167, '네 만날 수 있어요', 'Yes, I can meet (you then).', 'phrase', '1B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.1 SNU.lvl.1B SNU.lvl.1B.ch16'),
