(1189, 'N(이)라고 하다', 'to be called N', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1190, 'V(으)려고', 'so that/in order to', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1191, 'V거나', 'V or ...', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1192, 'N(이)나', '1. or (''or'' links N options)2. # whole Ns?! (SNU2Bch18; #''s/quantities are larger than typical)3. [I guess/how about] N or whatnot 4. then for plan B... (SNU3Ach4; making selection from acceptable 2nd choices or light suggestion)', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch18 SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3A SNU.lvl.3A.ch4'),
(1193, 'V는 것', 'V phrase now functions as N', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1194, 'V(으)ᄅ 줄 알다/모르다', 'to know/not know how to V', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1195, 'V(으)ㄴ N', 'N who/that Ved', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1196, 'A/V지 않다/못하다', 'not/didn''t A/V', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1197, 'V아/어 보다', 'Subj has tried/experienced V', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1198, '(time word)N 동안', 'for N''s amount of time', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1199, 'A(으)ㄴ데; V는데; N인데', '1. so (background info)2. because (unexpected) 3. but (contrast)', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1200, 'V(으)ㄹ N', 'N to V (future tense adnomial)', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1201, 'A(으)ᄂ; V는; N인 것 같다', 'I think, looks/seems like', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1202, 'N보다', 'than N (comparison)', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1203, 'A/V았/었으면 좋겠다', 'would be good if A/V', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1204, 'A/V(으)ᄅ까요?', 'do you think that? I wonder...?(ask for listeners opinion about something unknown)', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1205, 'A/V(으)ㄹ 거예요', 'I think I/it will A/V(indirect assumption/opinion)', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1206, 'A/V(으)니까; N(이)니까', 'because, since(cl. 1 is reason for cl.2; cannot be ''excuse'')', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1207, 'V고 나서', 'and then, after Ving completed, another action/event follows', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1208, 'N(이)라서', 'because it is N', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1209, '''르'' 불규칙', '''르'' drops ''ᅳ'', doubles ''ᄅ'' before 아/어 endings', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1210, 'V(으)면 되다', '1. you only have to, it''s enough if you 2. one can/it''s ok to', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1211, 'V(으)ㄴ 것 같다', 'I think, looks/seems like Ved(speculate about past events based on speaker''s perception)', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1212, 'A/V(으)ㄹ 것 같다', 'I think, looks/seems like will A/V(speculation/humble opinion)', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1213, 'V는지; N인지 알다/모르다', 'to know/not know if(asking/responding to ?s about knowing fact/method)', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1214, 'A/V았/었을 것 같다', 'probably A/Ved(speculation about past)', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1215, 'V(으)려면', 'if you want to V...then...(intention followed by condition necessary to satisfy)', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1216, 'V다가', '1. Was Ving when (interruption) 2. While Ving [st bad happened]1. V action interrupted by another action, subj of both clauses must be same (sometimes contracted to ''다'' 2. action of 1st cl. is basis/cause of negative situation in following cl. [abbr. -다]', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7 SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3A SNU.lvl.3A.ch8'),
(1217, 'A/V-겠-', '2nd/3rd pers. must/probably feel; 1st pers. will V', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1218, 'N 때문에', 'because of N', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1219, 'V아/어 버리다', '1. relied/dissatisfied that Ved 2. completely/totally V', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1220, 'A/V(으)ㄹ 때', 'time when A/V continues/occurs', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1221, 'A(으)ㄴ데요; V는데요; N인데요', 'A/V/N so... [expecting reaction/response; also can be rude: so what?! how about them apples?!]', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1222, 'V는 중이다; N 중이다on signs: N중', 'V/N in progress', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1223, 'A(으)ㄴ가요? V나요? N인가요?', 'gentle question', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1224, 'N밖에', 'outside of N, no other possibility/choice(w/ neg. only)', 'grammar', '2A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1225, 'N 중에(서)', 'among all the Ns', 'grammar', '2B', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1226, 'Location N에서', 'among all the places in N', 'grammar', '2B', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1227, '(으)니/니? & (으)냐/느냐?', '반말 ? form (for little kids)can NOT be used with superiors even w/ permission to speak in 반말', 'grammar', '2B', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1228, '-요 is dropped 이다= (이)야-아/어', '반말half words when social relationship is close, or talking to inferiors/younger people', 'grammar', '2B', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1229, 'V(으)ㄹ래요 (?)', '(?) want to V [immanent action/ shall we...?]as a statement: speakers intention, will', 'grammar', '2B', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1230, '''ᄉ'' 불규칙', 'ᄉ dropped before vowels', 'grammar', '2B', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1231, 'N마다', 'every/each N', 'grammar', '2B', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1232, 'V는 게 어때요?also: V아/어 보는 게 어떼요?', 'how about V?', 'grammar', '2B', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
