(1264, '저는 마이틀 존스라고 합니다.', 'I''m called Michael Jones.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1265, '저는 다나카 마리코라고 합니다.', 'I''m called Tanaka Mariko.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1266, '저는 최정우라고 합니다.', 'I''m called Choi Jong-woo.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1267, '저는 류 샤오밍이라고 합니다.', 'I''m called Ryu Shaoming.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1268, '저는 줄리앙 김이라고 합니다.', 'I''m called Julian Kim.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1269, '선생님을 만나려고 사무실에 갔어요.', 'So that I could meet the teacher, I went to the office.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1270, '책을 빌리려고 도서관에 갔어요.', 'In order to borrow a book, I went to the library.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1271, '약속을 하려고 전화를 했어요.', 'So that I could make an appointment, I made a call.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1272, '점심에 먹으려고 김밥을 샀어요.', 'So that I could eat lunch, I bought kimbap.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1273, '여권을 만들려고 사진을 찍었어요.', 'In order to make a passport, I took a picture.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1274, '집에서 쉬거나 친구를 만나요.', 'I rest at home or meet with friends.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1275, '운동을 하거나 친구를 만나요.', 'I''ll go workout or meet up with a friend.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1276, '우유를 마시거나 과일을 먹어요.', 'I drink milk or eat fruit.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1277, '걸어서 오거나 버스를 타요.', 'I walk or take the bus.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1278, '사전을 차거나 친구에게 물어봐요.', 'I search in the dictionary or ask a friend.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1279, '커피나 녹차 어때요?', 'Coffee or green tea, how about it?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1280, '불고기나 갈비 어때요?', 'How about bulgogi or galbi?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1281, '내일이나 모레 어때요?', 'How about tomorrow or the day after tomorrow?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1282, '꽃이나 과일 어때요?', 'Flowers or fruit, how about that?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1283, '명동이나 동대문시장 어때요?', 'Myeongdong or Dongdae Moon Market, how about it?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch1'),
(1284, '네 저는 수영하는 것을 좋아해요.', 'Yes, I like swimming.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1285, '네 저는 등산하는 것을 좋아해요.', 'Yes, I like hiking.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1286, '네 저는 영화 보는 것을 좋아해요.', 'Yes, I like watching movies.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1287, '네 저는 여행하는 것을 좋아해요.', 'Yes, I like traveling.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1288, '네 저는 음악 듣는 것을 조아해요.', 'Yes, I like listening to music.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1289, '운전을 할 줄 알지만 잘 못해요.', '(I) know how to drive, but not well.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1290, '스키를 탈 줄 알지만 잘 못 타요.', 'I know how to ski, but not well.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1291, '피아노를 칠 줄 알지만 잘 못 쳐요.', 'I know how to play the piano, but not well.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1292, '스페인어를 할 줄 알지만 잘 못해요.', 'I know how to speak Spanish, but not well.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1293, '한국 음식을 만들 줄 알지만 잘 못 만들어요.', 'I know how to make Korean food, but not well.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1294, '주말에 본 영화 어땠어요?', 'How was the movie (that) you saw last week?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1295, '어제 다녀온 콘서트 어땠어요?', 'Yesterday, the concert you went to, how was it?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1296, '정우가 소개해 준 친구 어땠어요?', 'The friend Jung-woo introduced, how is he?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1297, '어제 읽은 책 어땠어요?', 'How was the book (that) you read yesterday?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1298, '아침에 들은 수업 어땠어요?', 'How was the class you took this morning?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1299, '아니요 어렵지 않아요.', 'No, its not difficult.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1300, '아니요 맵지 않아요.', 'No, its not spicy.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1301, '아니요 크지 않아요.', 'No, it''s not big.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1302, '아니요 만나지 않아요.', 'No, I didn''t meet (anyone).', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1303, '아니요 가지 않았어요.', 'No, I didn''t go.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch2'),
(1304, '삼계탕을 먹어 봤어요?', 'Have you ever tried Samgyetang?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1305, '네, 먹어 봤어요.', 'Yes, I have tried (that food).', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1306, '아니요, 못 먹어 봤어요.', 'No, I haven''t been able to eat (that).', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1307, '불고기를 만들어 봤어요?', 'Have you ever tried making bulgogi?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1308, '네 만들어 봤어요.', 'Yes, I have tried making (bulgogi).', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1309, '부산에 가 봤어요?', 'Have you ever been to Busan?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1310, '아니요 못 가 봤어요.', 'No, I haven''t been able to go.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1311, '한국 음악을 들어 봤어요?', 'Have you ever heard Korean music?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1312, '네 들어 봤어요.', 'Yes, I''ve heard (Korean music).', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1313, '한복을 입어 봤어요?', 'Have you ever worn a hanbok?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1314, '아니요 못 입어 봤어요.', 'No, I haven''t been able to wear (that).', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1315, '날씨가 좋은데 산책할까요?', 'The weather is nice, so shall we go for a walk?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1316, '피곤한데 좀 쉴까요?', '(I''m) tired, so shall we take a little break?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1317, '날씨가 더운데 냉면을 먹을까요?', 'Since the weather is hot, shall we eat naengmyeon?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1318, '시간이 없는데 택시를 탈까요?', 'There''s no time, so shall we take a taxi?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1319, '내일이 휴일인데 등산하러 갈까요?', 'Tomorrow is a holiday, so shall we go hiking?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1320, '어제 명동에 갔는데 사람이 아주 많았어요.', 'Yesterday I went to Myeongdong and there were very many people.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1321, '토요일에 산에 갔는데 비가 왔어요.', 'Saturday I went to the mountain and it rained.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1322, '점심에 피자를 먹었는데 멋있었어요.', 'At lunch I ate pizza and it was delicious.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1323, '어제 영화를 봤는데 재미있었어요.', 'Yesterday (I) watched a movie and it was fun.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1324, '주말에 이 책을 읽었는데 좀 어려웠어요.', '(I) read this book over the weekend and it was a little difficult.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1325, '마실 물이 없어요.', 'There''s no water to drink.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1326, '먹을 음식이 없어요.', 'There''s no food to eat.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1327, '읽을 책이 많아요.', 'There are lots of books to read.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1328, '할 일이 있어요.', 'I have work to do.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1329, '입을 옷이 없어요.', 'I don''t have anything to wear.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch3'),
(1330, '숙제하는 것 같아요.', 'Seems like she''s doing homework.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1331, '방에서 자는 것 같아요.', 'Seems like he''s sleeping in his room.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1332, '아주 바쁜 것 같아요.', 'I think she''s very busy.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1333, '집에 있는 것 같아요.', 'I think he''s at home.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1334, '어제보다 추운 것 같아요.', 'It seems colder than yesterday.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1335, '줄리앙 씨 동생인 것 같아요.', 'I think he''s Julian''s younger sibling.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1336, '유진 씨 가방인 것 같아요.', 'Seems like it''s Eujin''s bag.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1337, '다음 주 목요일인 것 같아요.', 'I think it''s next Thursday.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1338, '프랑스 사람인 것 같아요.', 'I think he''s French.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1339, '3층인 것 같아요.', 'I think its on the 3rd floor.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1340, '지하철이 버스보다 더 복잡해요.', 'The subway is more crowded than the bus.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1341, '오늘이 어제보다 더 바빠요.', 'Today (I''m) busier than yesterday.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1342, '올해가 작년보다 더 더워요.', 'This year is hotter than last year.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1343, '쓰기가 읽기보다 더 어려워요.', 'Writing is more difficult than reading.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1344, '한라산이 설악산보다 더 높아요.', 'Mt. Halla is taller than Mt. Seorak.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1345, '한국 친구가 있었으면 좋겠어요.', 'I wish I had a Korean friend.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1346, '한국말을 잘했으면 좋겠어요.', 'I wish I could speak Korean well.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1347, '돈이 많았으면 좋겠어요.', 'It would be good if I had a lot of money.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1348, '숙제가 없었으면 좋겠어요.', 'I wish I didn''t have homework.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1349, '집이 가까웠으면 좋겠어요.', 'I wish my house was close.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch4'),
(1350, '내일 날씨가 좋을까요?', 'Do you know if the weather will be good tomorrow?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1351, '지금 가면 늦을까요?', 'If we go now, do you think we will be late?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1352, '도서관에 자리가 있을까요?', 'Do you know if there are seats at the library?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1353, '이 영화가 무서울까요?', 'Would this movie be scary?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1354, '나나 씨가 집에 도착했을까요?', 'I wonder if Nana got home.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1355, '네 올 거예요.', 'Yes, I think (she) will come.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1356, '아니요 안 올 거에요.', 'No, I don''t think (she) will come.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1357, '네 막힐 거에요.', 'Yes, there will be traffic.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1358, '아니요 없을 거예요.', 'No, I don''t think (he''s there).', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1359, '네 어울릴 거예요.', 'Yes, it''ll look good on you.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1360, '아니요 안 매울 거에요.', 'No, it won''t be spicy', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1361, '길이 복잡하니까 지하철을 타요.', 'The roads are congested so I take the subway.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1362, '오늘은 바쁘니까 내일 만나요.', 'I''m busy today, so lets meet tomorrow', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1363, '백화점은 비싸니까 시장에서 사요.', 'Department stores are expensive, so shop at a market.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1364, '여기에서 가까우니까 걸어서 가요.', 'It''s close to here so let''s walk.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1365, '오늘 시험이 끝났이니까 같이 영화 봐요.', 'Today exams are finished so lets watch a movie together.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1366, '저녁을 먹고 나서 텔레비전을 봤어요.', 'I ate dinner and then watched TV.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1367, '영화를 보고 나서 친구와 이야기했어요.', 'I talked to my friend after watching a movie.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1368, '운동하고 나서 샤워했어요.', 'I took a shower after working out.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1369, '손을 씻고 나서 밥을 먹었어요.', 'I washed my hands and then ate a meal.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1370, '문자를 받고 나서 전화했어요.', 'I got the text and then called you. I called you after I got the text.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch5'),
(1371, '버스로 가요.', '(I) go by bus.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1372, '문자로 연락해요.', 'I contact (my friends) through text.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1373, '우편으로 보내요.', 'I send (my application) through the mail.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1374, '인터넷으로 사요.', 'I buy (my books) through the internet.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1375, '친구들과 어느 나라 말로 이야기해요?', 'What language do you speak with your friends?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1376, '한국말로 이야기해요.', '(We) speak in Korean.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1377, '아니요 내일은 휴일이라서 열지 않을 거예요.', 'No, tomorrow is a holiday, so it won''t be open.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1378, '아니요 지금은 방학이라서 많지 않을 거예요.', 'No, it''s school break now, so there won''t be many (people).', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1379, '아니요 지금은 수업 시간이라서 받지 않을 거예요.', 'No, it''s class time right now, so she won''t take it (answer her phone).', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1380, '아니요 이번 주가 휴가라서 없을 거예요.', 'No, this week is a vacation so (he) won''t be there.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1381, '아니요 내일이 추석이라서 없을 거예요.', 'No, tomorrow is Chuseok so there won''t be any (train tickets).', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1382, '아니요 금요일까지 하면 돼요.', 'No, it''s ok if you do it by Friday.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1383, '아니요 다음 주까지 끝내면 돼요.', 'No, it''s ok if you finish it by next week.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1384, '아니요 모레까지 내면 돼요.', 'No, you can just submit (the photo) by the day after tomorrow.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1385, '아니요 열 시까지 도착하면 돼요.', 'No, you can just arrive by 10.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1386, '아니요 내일 밤까지 보내면 돼요.', 'No, we can just send it by tomorrow night.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1387, '집에 간 것 같아요.', 'I think (she) went home.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1388, '감기에 걸린 것 같아요.', 'I think I caught a cold.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1389, '수업이 일찍 끝난 것 같아요.', 'Seems like the class ended early.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1390, '조금 전에 시작한 것 같아요.', 'Seems like (the class) started a little while ago.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1391, '시험을 잘 본 것 같아요.', 'I think I did well on my test.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch6'),
(1392, '날씨가 좋을 것 같아요.', 'I think the weather will be nice.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1393, '비가 올 것 같아요.', 'It looks like it might rain.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1394, '이 신발이 편할 것 같아요.', 'These shoes seem like they will be comfortable.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1395, '저 책이 재미있을 것 같아요.', 'I think that book will be interesting.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1396, '시험이 어려울 것 같아요.', 'Sounds like the test will be difficult.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1397, '교실이 어디인지 아세요?', 'Do you know where the classroom is?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1398, '숙제가 뭔지 아세요?', 'Do you know what the homework is?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1399, '책값이 얼마인지 아세요?', 'Do you know how much the book costs?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1400, '지금이 몇 시인지 아세요?', 'Do you know what time it is right now?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1401, '사무실이 몇 층인지 아세요?', 'Do you know what floor the office is on?', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1402, '서울대에 가려면 지하철 2호선을 타세요', 'If you want to go to Seoul National University, take subway line 2.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1403, '책을 빌리려면 학생증을 만드세요', 'If you want to borrow a book, make a student ID card.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1404, '발음을 잘하려면 큰 소리로 많이 읽으세요', 'If you want to pronounce well, read out loud a lot.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1405, '한국말을 배우려면 언어교육원에 등록하세요', 'If you want to learn Korean, register for the language institute.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1406, '늦지 않으려면 택시를 타세요', 'If you don''t want to be late, take a taxi.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1407, '숙제를 하다가 잤어요', 'I was doing my homework but then I fell asleep.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1408, '영화를 보다가 울었어요', 'I cried while watching a movie.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1409, '학교에 가다가 친구를 만났어요', 'I was going to school when I met a friend. I met a friend on my way to school.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1410, '밥을 먹다가 전화를 받았어요', 'I was eating a meal when I got a phone call. I got a call while I was eating.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1411, '서울에서 살다가 부산으로 이사 갔어요', 'I was living in Seoul when I moved to Busan.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch7'),
(1412, '피곤하겠네요', 'You must be tired.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1413, '기쁘겠네요', 'You must be happy.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1414, '속상하겠네요', 'You must be upset/feel awful.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1415, '걱정되겠네요', 'You must be worried.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1416, '좋겠네요', 'Sounds good!', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1417, '감기 때문에 못 왔어요', 'I couldn''t come because of a cold.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1418, '일 때문에 못 했어요', 'Because of work I couldn''t do it.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1419, '버스 때문에 늦었어요', 'Because of the bus, I was late.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1420, '숙제 때문에 못 갔어요', 'I couldn''t go because of homework.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1421, '날씨 때문에 못 했어요', 'I couldn''t do it because of the weather.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1422, '아니요 다 먹어 버렸어요', 'No, I ate all of it (there''s none left).', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1423, '아니요 놓쳐 버렸어요', 'No, I completely missed (the bus)! :(', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1424, '아니요 잊어버렸어요', 'No, I completely forgot! :(', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1425, '아니요 잃어버렸어요', 'No, I''m afraid I lost it. :(', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1426, '아니요 다 써 버렸어요', 'No, I totally used all (of my money). :(', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1427, '맛있는 음식을 먹을 때 기뿐이 좋아요', 'I feel good when eating delicious food.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1428, '친구가 거짓말할 때 화가 나요', 'When my friend lies, I get angry.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1429, '집에 혼자 있을 때 외로워요', 'I feel lonely when home alone.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1430, '몸이 아플 때 가고 싶어요', 'I want to go (to my hometown) when I feel sick.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1431, '사람들 앞에서 발표할 때 긴장돼요', 'When presenting in front of people, I feel nervous.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch8'),
(1432, '옷을 바꾸러 왔는데요', 'I came to exchange some clothes.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1433, '소포를 보내러 왔는데요', 'I came to send a package.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1434, '김 선생님을 만나러 왔는데요', 'I came here to meet Mrs. Kim.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1435, '학생증을 찾으러 왔는데요', 'I came to look for my student ID.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1436, '통장을 만들러 왔는데요', 'I came to open a bank account.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1437, '지금 출장 중인데요', 'Right now she''s in the middle of a business trip.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1438, '지금 회의 중인데요', 'Right now I''m in the middle of a meeting.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1439, '지금 통화 중인데요', 'Right now the line''s busy.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1440, '지금 수업 중인데요', 'I''m in the middle of class right now.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1441, '지금 휴가 중인데요', 'I''m on vacation right now. Right now I''m in the middle of a vacation.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1442, '기차가 몇 시에 도착하나요?', 'What time does the train arrive? (gentle)', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1443, '내일 학교에 가나요?', 'Are you going to school tomorrow? (gentle)', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1444, '밖에 비가 오나요?', 'Is it raining outside? (gentle)', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1445, '어떤 책을 읽고 있나요?', 'What kind of book are you reading? (gentle)', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1446, '기숙사에 사나요?', 'Do you live in the dorms? (gentle)', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1447, '아니요 한 시간밖에 안 했어요', 'No, I only did 1 hour (of work/studying).', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1448, '아니요 세 명밖에 언 왔어요', 'No, no more than 3 people came.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1449, '아니요 네 시간밖에 안 잤어요', 'No, I only slept 4 hours.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1450, '아니요 한 잔밖에 안 마셨어요', 'No, I drank no more than one glass.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1451, '아니요 두 번밖에 안 봤어요', 'No, I''ve only seen (a movie) two times.', 'phrase', '2A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2A SNU.lvl.2A.ch9'),
(1452, '한국 음식 중에서 비빔밥이 제일 맛있어.', 'Out of all Korean food, bibimbap is the most delicious. (casual)', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1453, '꽃 중에서 장미가 제일 예뻐.', 'Among flowers, the rose is the prettiest. (casual)', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1454, '한국 노래 중에서 이 노래가 제일 좋아.', 'Out of all Korean songs, this song is the best. (casual)', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1455, '일주일 중에서 월요일이 제일 바빠.', 'Among days of the week, Monday is the busiest. (casual)', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1456, '우리 반 학생 중에서 샤오밍 씨가 제일 멋있어.', 'Shoaming is the coolest student in our class. (casual)', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1457, '몇 시에 일어나?', 'What time do you wake up? (casual)', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1458, '음악을 자주 들어?', 'Do you listen to music often? (casual)', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1459, '집이 여기서 멀어?', 'Is your house far from here? (casual)', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1460, '지난 주말에 뭐 했어?', 'What did you do last weekend? (casual)', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1461, '이번 방학에 어디에 갈 거야?', 'Where are you going this vacation? (casual)', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1462, '주말에 도서관에 갈래요?', 'Do you want to go to the library on the weekend?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1463, '이번 방학에 제주도에 갈래요?', 'Do you want to go to Jeju Island this vacation?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1464, '저녁에 학교 앞에서 만날래요?', 'Do you want to meet in front of the school in the evening?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1465, '일요일에 우리 집에 올래요?', 'Do you want to come to my house on Sunday?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1466, '점심에 비빔밥을 먹을래요?', 'Do you want to eat bibimbap at lunch?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1467, '축구는 잘하는데 농구는 잘 못해요.', 'I''m good at soccer, but I''m not good at basketball.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1468, '김치는 좋아하는데 김치찌개는 안 좋아해요.', 'I like kimchi but I don''t like kimchi stew.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1469, '버스 정류장은 가까운데 지하철역은 멀어요.', 'The bus stop is close, but the subway station is far.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1470, '얼굴은 아는데 이름은 몰라요.', 'I know his face, but I don''t know his name.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1471, '아침에는 비가 왔는데 지금은 안 와요.', 'It rained in the morning, but not now.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch10'),
(1472, '아침마다 운동을 해요.', 'Every morning I work out.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1473, '주말마다 등산을 가요.', 'I go hiking every weekend.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1474, '수요일마다 태권도를 배워요.', 'I learn taekwondo every Wednesday.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1475, '쉬는 시간마다 친구를 만나요.', 'I meet my friends every break.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1476, '여섯 시간마다 약을 먹어요.', 'I take medicine every six hours.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1477, '시간이 있을 때마다 음악을 들어요.', 'I listen to music whenever I have time.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1478, '영화를 볼 때마다 팝콘을 먹어요.', 'I eat popcorn every time I watch a movie.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1479, '눈이 아플 때마다 안약을 넣어요.', 'Whenever my eyes hurt I put in eye drops.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1480, '이 음악을 들을 때마다 고향 생각이 나요.', 'Every time I listen to this music, I think of my hometown.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1481, '가족이 보고 싶을 때마다 전화를 해요.', 'Whenever I miss my family I call them.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1482, '약을 먹는 게 어때요?', 'How about taking some medicine?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1483, '병원에 가는 게 어때요?', 'How about going to the hospital?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1484, '커피를 줄이는 게 어때요?', 'How about reducing your coffee intake?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1485, '운동을 좀 해 보는 게 어때요?', 'How about you try a little exercise?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1486, '전화를 해 보는 게 어때요?', 'How about trying to make a call?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1487, '친구와 여행 가기로 했어요.', 'I promised a friend I would go on a trip.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1488, '제주도로 가기로 했어요.', 'I decided to go to Jeju-do.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1489, '열 시에 만나기로 했어요.', 'I promised to meet up at 10:00.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1490, '가족들과 저녁을 먹기로 했어요.', 'I promised to have dinner with my family.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1491, '친구들과 놀기로 했어요.', 'I promised to hang out with my friends.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch11'),
(1492, '옷이 편해 보여요.', 'Your cloths look comfortable.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1493, '성격이 좋아 보여요.', 'You look like you have a good personality.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1494, '키가 커 보여요.', 'She looks tall.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1495, '영화가 재미있어 보여요.', 'The movie looks interesting.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1496, '문제가 어려워 보여요.', 'The problem looks difficult.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1497, '네 저도 스티븐 씨처럼 친구가 많았으면 좋겠어요.', 'Yes, I wish I had a lot of friends like Stephen.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1498, '네 저도 마리코 씨처럼 요리를 잘했으면 좋겠어요.', 'I wish I could cook as well as Mariko', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1499, '네 저도 켈리 씨처럼 성격이 활발했으면 좋겠어요.', 'Yes, I wish I had an outgoing personality like Kelly.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1500, '네 저도 줄리앙 씨처럼 기타를 잘 쳤으면 좋겠어요.', 'Yes, I wish I could play the guitar well like Julian.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12');
INSERT INTO vocab (id, korean, english, word_type, level, tags) VALUES
(1501, '네 저도 샤오밍 씨처럼 키가 컸으면 좋겠어요.', 'Yes, I wish I were as tall as Shaoming.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1502, '네 많은 편이에요.', 'Yes there tends to be a lot.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1503, '네 비싼 편이에요.', 'Yes, it tends to be expensive.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1504, '네 조용한 편이에요.', 'Yes, I tend to be quiet.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1505, '네 열심히 하는 편이에요.', 'Yes, I tend to work hard.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1506, '네 재미있는 편이에요.', 'Yes, it tends to be fun.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1507, '네 재미있게 봤어요.', 'Yes, I joyfully watched it.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1508, '네 맛있게 먹었어요.', 'Yes, I ate it deliciously.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1509, '네 싸게 샀어요.', 'Yes, I bought it cheap.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1510, '네 쉽게 구했어요.', 'Yes, I got it easily.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1511, '네 개끗하게 했어요.', 'Yes, I cleanly did it.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch12'),
(1512, '글쎄요 재미있을지 모르겠어요.', 'Well, I don''t know if it''ll be fun.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1513, '글쎄요 있을지 모르겠어요.', 'Well, I don''t know if there is [a vacancy at the library].', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1514, '글쎄요 좋을지 모르겠어요.', 'Well, I don''t know if it''ll be good.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1515, '글쎄요 올 수 있을지 모르겠어요.', 'Well, I don''t know if she can come.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1516, '글쎄요 일찍 도착할 수 있을지 모르겠어요.', 'Well, I don''t know if [s/he] can get there early.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1517, '힘들기는 하지만 재미있어요.', 'True, it''s hard, but it''s fun.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1518, '맵기는 하지만 맛있어요.', 'True, it''s spicy, but it''s delicious.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1519, '피곤하기는 하지만 괜찮아요.', 'True, I''m tired, but it''s ok.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1520, '비싸기는 하지만 시설이 잘되어 있어요.', 'It''s true that it''s expensive, but the facilities are good.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1521, '여행 가고 싶기는 하지만 시간이 없어요.', 'It''s true I want to go on a trip, but I don''t have time.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1522, '여기는 교통이 편리하기 때문에 집값이 비싸요.', 'Because the transportation is convenient here, the housing prices are expensive.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1523, '이 집은 넓기 때문에 두 사람이 살 수 있어요.', 'Because this house is large, two people can live [in it].', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1524, '음식이 맛있기 때문에 그 식당에 자주 가요.', 'Because the food is delicious I go to that restaurant often.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1525, '주말에 사람이 많기 때문에 예약해야 해요.', 'Because there are a lot of people on the weekend, you have to make a reservation.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1526, '지금 휴가 기간이기 때문에 비행기 표 사기가 어려워요.', 'Because it''s a vacation time period right now, its hard to get a plane ticket.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1527, '시장이 멀어서 장을 보기가 불편해요.', 'The market is far away so grocery shopping [there] is inconvenient.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1528, '지하철역이 가까워서 학교 가기가 편해요.', 'The subway station is close so going to school is convenient.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1529, '주변이 조용해서 살기가 좋아요.', 'The neighborhood is quiet so its a good place to live.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1530, '모르는 단어가 많아서 읽기가 어려워요.', 'There are so many words I don''t know, so reading is difficult.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1531, '친구가 너무 바빠서 만나기가 힘들어요.', 'My friend is so busy that it''s difficult to meet with him.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch13'),
(1532, '아니요 전에 간 적이 있어요.', 'No, I''ve had the experience of going (there) before.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1533, '아니요 전에 본 적이 있어요.', 'No, I''ve had the experience of seeing (it) before.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1534, '아니요 전에 먹은 적이 있어요.', 'No, I''ve had the experience of eating (that) before.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1535, '아니요 전에 만난 적이 있어요.', 'No, I''ve had the experience of meeting (her) before.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1536, '아니요 전에 들은 적이 있어요.', 'No, I''ve had the experience of listening [to it] before.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1537, '어렸을 때 봤어요.', 'When I was young (a child) I saw him.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1538, '장학금을 받았을 때 기뻤어요.', 'When I received the scholarship I was happy.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1539, '할머니가 돌아가셨을 때 슬펐어요.', 'When my grandmother died, I was sad.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1540, '고향에 갔을 때 들었어요.', 'I heard it when I went to my hometown.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1541, '집에 도착했을 때 받았어요.', 'I received it when I got home.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1542, '여기에서 사진을 찍어도 돼요?', 'Can I take a picture here?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1543, '지금 나가도 돼요?', 'Can I leave now?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1544, '밤에 전화해도 돼요?', 'Can I call you at night?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1545, '이 컴퓨터를 써도 돼요?', 'Can I use this computer?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1546, '여기에서 음식을 먹어도 돼요?', 'Can I eat food here?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1547, '아니요 사진을 찍으면 안 돼요.', 'No, you can''t take a picture.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1548, '아니요 주차해면 안 돼요.', 'No, you can''t park (your car).', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1549, '아니요 담배를 피우면 안 돼요.', 'No, you can''t smoke a cigarette.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1550, '아니요 음료수를 마시면 안 돼요.', 'No, you can''t drink a beverage.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1551, '아니요 노래를 부르면 안 돼요.', 'No, you can''t sing a song.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch14'),
(1552, '1급보다 어려워졌어요.', '(It''s) gotten harder than level 1.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1553, '겨울보다 싸졌어요.', '(It''s) gotten cheaper than in winter.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1554, '작년보다 바빠졌어요.', '(I''ve) gotten busier than last year.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1555, '전보다 좋아졌어요.', 'It''s gotten better than before.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1556, '어제보다 추워졌어요.', 'It''s gotten colder than yesterday.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1557, '아니요 한국에 와서 좋아하게 되었어요.', 'No, I came to Korea and ended up liking it [kimchi].', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1558, '아니요 한국에 와서 배우게 되었어요.', 'No, since coming to Korea I ended up learning [it] (Korean).', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1559, '아니요 한국에 와서 가르치게 되었어요.', 'No, I came to Korea and ended up teaching.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1560, '아니요 한국에 와서 하게 되었어요.', 'No, since coming to Korea I ended up doing [it] (cooking).', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1561, '아니요 한국에 와서 혼자 살게 되었어요.', 'No, I came to Korea and ended up living alone.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1562, '자기 전에 이를 닦아요.', 'Before sleeping, (I) brush my teeth.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1563, '밥 먹기 전에 손을 씻어요.', 'Before a meal (I) wash (my) hands.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1564, '결혼식에 가기 전에 선물을 준비해요.', 'Before going to the wedding ceremony, (I) prepare a gift.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1565, '방학이 끝나기 전에 여행을 가고 싶어요.', 'Before the school break is over (I) want to go on a trip.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1566, '친구들이 오기 전에 음식을 준비해야 해요.', 'Before friends come (I) need to prepare food.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1567, '일을 긑낸 후에 볼 거에요.', 'After work ends I will see it.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1568, '점심을 먹은 후에 만날 거에요.', 'After eating lunch (I) will meet up.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1569, '설거지한 후에 할 거에요.', 'After washing the dishes I will do it.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1570, '한국어 공부를 마친 후에 돌아갈 거에요.', 'After (I) finish studying Korean I will go back.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1571, '숙제를 다 한 후에 먹을 거에요.', 'After doing all my homework I will eat.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch15'),
(1572, '네 벌써 사 놓았어요.', 'Yes, (I''ve) already bought it. (for use later)', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1573, '네 벌써 찍어 놓았어요.', 'Yes, (I''ve) already taken [the picture]. (it''s still taken)', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1574, '네 벌써 써 놓았어요.', 'Yes, (I''ve) already written it. (it''s still written)', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1575, '네 벌써 예약해 놓았어요.', 'Yes, (I''ve) already made the reservation. (ahead of time)', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1576, '네 벌써 만들어 놓았어요.', 'Yes, (I''ve) already made it. (it''s still made)', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1577, '여필 대신 볼펜을 샀어요.', 'Instead of a pencil, (I) bought a pen.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1578, '버스 대신 택시를 탔어요.', 'Instead of the bus (I) took a taxi.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1579, '주소 대신 전화번호를 가르쳐줬어요.', 'Instead of the address (I''ll) tell you the phone number.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1580, '친구 대신 제가 전화를 했어요.', 'Instead of my friend I made the phone call.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1581, '동생 대신 제가 운전을 했어요.', 'Instead of my younger sibling, I did the driving.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1582, '여행을 갈까 해요.', '(I''m) considering going on a trip.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1583, '집에서 쉴까 해요.', '(I''m) thinking about resting at home.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1584, '영화를 볼까 해요.', '(I''m) thinking of watching a movie.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1585, '김밥을 먹을까 해요.', '(I''m) considering eating kimbap.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1586, '원피스를 입을까 해요.', '(I''m) thinking I''ll wear a dress.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1587, '내가 운전할 테니까 쉬세요.', 'I insist on driving, take a rest.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1588, '빨리 갈 테니까 기다리세요.', 'I''ll be there soon, hold on.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1589, '내가 도와줄 테니까 걱정하지 마세요.', 'I insist I''ll help, so don''t worry.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1590, '지금은 전화를 안 받을 테니까 나중에 전화하세요.', 'I''m really not answering right now, so call me later.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1591, '날씨가 추울 테니까 따뜻하게 입으세요.', 'I really think it''s going to be cold, so dress warmly.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch16'),
(1592, '부모님을 공항에 모셔다 드렸어요.', '(I) took (my) parents to the airport.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1593, '동생을 유치원에 데려다 주었어요.', '(I) took (my) younger sibling to kindergarten.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1594, '어머니를 병원에 모셔다 드렸어요.', '(I) took (my) mother to the hospital.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1595, '할아버지를 댁에 모셔다 드렸어요.', '(I) brought (my) grandfather home.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1596, '아이를 학교에 데려다 주었어요.', '(I) took (my) child to school.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1597, '영화를 보다가 울 뻔했어요.', '(I) almost cried watching a movie.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1598, '요리를 하다가 불이 날 뻔했어요.', 'A fire almost broke out while cooking.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1599, '길을 건너다가 사고가 날 뻔했어요.', '(I) almost got into an accident crossing the street.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1600, '버스에서 내리다가 넘어질 뻔했어요.', '(I) almost fell down while getting off the bus.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1601, '바다에서 수영을 하다가 죽을 뻔했어요.', '(I) almost died swimming in the sea.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1602, '왜 그렇게 얼굴이 노래요?', 'Why is (your) face so yellow?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1603, '왜 그렇게 팔이 까매요?', 'Why are (your) arms so dark?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1604, '왜 그렇게 눈이 빨개요?', 'Why are (your) eyes so red?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1605, '왜 그렇게 입술이 파래요?', 'Why are (your) lips so blue?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1606, '왜 그렇게 얼굴이 하얘요?', 'Why is (your) face so white?', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1607, '꽃병이 책상 위에 놓여 있어요.', '(There''s) a vase put on the desk.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1608, '시계가 벽에 걸려 있어요.', '(There''s) a clock hanging on the wall.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1609, '인형이 가방에 달려 있어요.', '(There''s) a doll hanging on the bag.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1610, '아이가 침대에 누워 있어요.', 'The child is lying in bed.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1611, '동생이 아버지 옆에 앉아 있어요.', '(My) younger sibling is sitting next to father.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch17'),
(1612, '한국에 온 지 다섯 달 됐어요.', 'It''s been five months since I came to Korea.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch18'),
(1613, '아침을 먹은 지 세 시간 됐어요.', 'It''s been three hours since I ate breakfast.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch18'),
(1614, '안경을 쓴 지 오 년 됐어요.', 'Been wearing glasses since 5 years ago.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch18'),
(1615, '서울에서 산 지 삼 개 월 됐어요.', 'Been living in Seoul for three months.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch18'),
(1616, '그 친구를 안 만난 지 두 달 됐어요.', 'Haven''t met up with that friend in two months.', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch18'),
(1617, '스무 명이나 있어요?', 'There''s 20 whole people here?!', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch18'),
(1618, '세 시간이나 운동해요?', 'You exercised for 3 whole hours?!', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch18'),
(1619, '십 년이나 됐어요?', 'It''s been 10 whole years?!', 'phrase', '2B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.2 SNU.lvl.2B SNU.lvl.2B.ch18'),
