(1643, 'V아어 달라고 하다', 'subj. asked to get stindirectly quote ''주세요'' request - speaker is recipient', 'grammar', '3A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3A SNU.lvl.3A.ch2'),
