(1659, 'V지 그래요?', 'why don''t you/why not...?weak imperative, suggestion or advice (NOT with superiors) ''why don''t you/why not...?''', 'grammar', '3A', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3A SNU.lvl.3A.ch5'),
