(1706, 'V고 보니(까)', 'after Ving I realize...come to know st or feel differently about st after an action (also feelings of resignation/acceptance)', 'grammar', '3B', 'Korean_grammar SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
