(1888, '중간시험이 끝나자마자 동아리 모임을 해요.', 'As soon as the midterms finish the club gets together.', 'phrase', '3A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3A SNU.lvl.3A.ch2'),
