(1894, '일하느라고 못 먹었어요.', 'Because I was working I couldn''t eat.', 'phrase', '3A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3A SNU.lvl.3A.ch2'),
(1895, '회의 준비하느라고 못 갔어요.', 'Because I was preparing for the meeting I couldn''t go.', 'phrase', '3A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3A SNU.lvl.3A.ch2'),
(1896, '공부하느라고 힘들어요.', 'Because of studying it''s hard.', 'phrase', '3A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3A SNU.lvl.3A.ch2'),
(1897, '면접 준비하느라고 바빠요.', 'Because interview prep I''m busy.', 'phrase', '3A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3A SNU.lvl.3A.ch2'),
(1898, '친구 만나고 오느라고 늦었어요.', 'I met up my friend so I was late.', 'phrase', '3A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3A SNU.lvl.3A.ch2'),
(1899, '우리 학교 학생은 누구나 열심히 공부해요.', 'every student in school studies hard.', 'phrase', '3A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3A SNU.lvl.3A.ch2'),
(1900, '마리코 씨는 언제나 제일 일찍 와요.', 'Every time Mariko comes earliest.', 'phrase', '3A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3A SNU.lvl.3A.ch2'),
