(1902, '시장은 어디나 사람이 많아요.', 'Everywhere in the market there''s a lot of people.', 'phrase', '3A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3A SNU.lvl.3A.ch2'),
(1903, '요즘 아이들은 누구나 컴퓨터 게임을 좋아해요.', 'All kids like computer days these days.', 'phrase', '3A', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3A SNU.lvl.3A.ch2'),
