(2061, '차를 바꾸려면 아직 멀었어요.', 'There''s still a long way to go before getting a new car.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch10'),
(2062, '이사하려면 아직 멀었어요.', 'Moving is still a long way off.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch10'),
(2063, '대학원을 졸업하려면 아직 멀었어요.', 'Graduating graduate school is still a long way off.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch10'),
(2064, '제가 신겨 주었어요.', 'I put shoes on him.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2065, '제가 벗겨 주었어요.', 'I undressed [the baby].', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2066, '제가 먹여 주었어요.', 'I fed her.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2067, '제가 태워 주었어요.', 'I gave her a ride.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2068, '제가 앉혀 주었어요.', 'I sat him.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2069, '우리 아기에게 씌우면 예쁠 것 같아요.', 'If we dress our baby [in that hat] I think she will look pretty.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2070, '내 동생에게 입히면 어울릴 것 같아요.', 'If you dress my younger brother [in that] I think it will look good on him.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2071, '제 조가에게 신기면 잘 맞을 것 같아요.', 'If you put [shoes] on my niece, I think it will suit her well.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2072, '민수 씨에게 맡기면 좋을 것 같아요.', 'If you leave it to Minsu, I think it would be good.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2073, '부모님께 알리면 기빠하실 것 같아요.', 'If you let your parents know I think they will be happy.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2074, '만약에 내일 비가 온다면 공연이 취소될 거예요.', 'If it rains tomorrow the show will be cancelled.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2075, '만약에 내일 모임에 늦게 간다면 사장님이 화를 내실 거예요.', 'If you go to the meeting late tomorrow, the boss will be angry.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2076, '만약에 생일 파티를 해 준다면 스티븐이 좋아할 거예요.', 'If you throw a party, Steven will like it.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2077, '만약에 먼저 사과한다면 여자 친구도 이해해 줄 거예요.', 'If you apologize first, your girlfriend will understand.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2078, '만약에 지하철에 놓고 내렸다면 분실물 센터에 있을 거예요.', 'If you left it on the subway, it will be at the lost and found center.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2079, '저는 어디든지 다 괜찮아요.', 'Anywhere is ok with me.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2080, '저는 언제든지 다 괜찮아요.', 'Anytime is ok with me.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2081, '저는 누구든지 다 괜찮아요.', 'Anyone is ok with me.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2082, '저는 무슨 선물이든지 다 괜찮아요.', 'Any gift is ok with me.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2083, '저는 무슨 음식이든지 다 괜찮아요.', 'Any food is ok with me.', 'phrase', '3B', 'Korean_pattern_practice SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch11'),
(2084, '약속 시간에 늦게 갔더니 화를 냈어요.', 'I was late for an appointment and so I got angry.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2085, '약을 먹었더니 열이 내렸어요.', 'I took medicine and so my fever went down.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2086, '카메라를 떨이뜨렸더니 고장 났어요.', 'I dropped the camera and so it broke.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2087, '아까 밥을 먹었더니 배가 안 고파요.', 'I ate a little while ago and so I''m not hungry.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2088, '비행기를 오래 탔더니 괴가 아파도.', 'I was riding a plane for along time and so my ears hurt.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2089, '얼마나 맛있는지 몰라요.', 'I don''t even know how delicious!', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2090, '얼마나 재미있는지 몰라요.', 'I don''t even know how much fun!', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2091, '얼마나 좋은지 몰라요.', 'I don''t even know how good!', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2092, '얼마나 어려운지 물라요.', 'I don''t even know how difficult!', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2093, '얼마나 많은지 몰라요', 'I don''t even know how many!', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2094, '요즘 운동을 하는 모양이에요.', 'Working out these days is the shape of it.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2095, '일이 많은 모양이에요.', 'A lot of work is the shape of it.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2096, '잠을 자는 모양이에요.', 'Taking a nap is the shape of it.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2097, '우등상을 받은 모양이에요.', 'Winning the honor student award is the shape of it.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2098, '값이 싼 모양이에요.', 'Cheap prices are the shape of it.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2099, '매일 연습해야 잘할 수 있어요.', 'You have to practice every day to be able to do well.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2100, '열심히 운동해야 건강해질 수 있어요.', 'You have to work out hard to be able to become healthy.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2101, '이터넷으로 예약해야 싸게 갈 수 있어요.', 'You have to make a reservation on the internet to be able to go there cheaply.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2102, '집을 많이 보러 다녀야 구할 수 있어요.', 'You have to go to see a lot of houses to be able to find one.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2103, '한국어를 잘해야 취직할 수 있어요.', 'You have to be good at Korean to be able to get a job.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNu.lvl.3B.ch12'),
(2104, '비가 올까 봐 우산을 가져가요.', 'I''m afraid it might rain, so I''ll bring an umbrella.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2105, '밤에 잠이 안 올까 봐 커피를 안 마셔요.', 'I don''t drink coffee at night because I''m afraid I won''t be able to sleep.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2106, '행사 준비가 제대로 안될까 봐 걱정이에요.', 'I''m afraid the event preparation isn''t done properly so I''m worried.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2107, '길이 막힐까 봐 일찍 나가요.', 'I''m afraid there will be traffic so I''ll leave early.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2108, '아침에 일찍 못 일어닐까 봐 잠을 못 잤어요.', 'I couldn''t sleep because I was afraid I wouldn''t be able to get up early in the morning.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2109, '파란색 바지를 입고 있는 사람이 스티븐 씨예요.', 'The person in the blue pants is Mr. Steven.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2110, '모자를 쓰고 있는 사람이 지연 씨예요.', 'The person wearing the hat is Mr. Jiyeon.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2111, '하늘색 넥타이를 매고 있는 사람이 아키라 씨예요.', 'The person wearing the sky blue tie is Mr. Akira.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2112, '회색 가방을 들고 있는 사람이 우리 오빠예요.', 'The person holding the gray bag is my brother.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2113, '목걸이와 귀걸이를 하고 있는 사람이 제 동생이에요.', 'The person wearing the necklace and earrings is my younger sibling.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2114, '죄송해요 미리 예약했어야 했는데.', 'Sorry, I should have booked in advance.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2115, '발표 준비를 제대로 했어야 했는데.', 'I should have prepared properly for the presentation.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2116, '원고를 미리 써 왔어야 했는데.', 'I should have written the manuscript in advance', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2117, '출발하기 전에 전화를 했어야 했는데.', 'I should have called before leaving.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2118, '회의 시간을 알려 드렸어야 했는데.', 'I should have given you the meeting time', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2119, '그럼 감기에 걸리지 않도록 손을 자주 씻으세요.', 'Then, to not catch a cold, wash your hands often.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2120, '상하지 않도록 냉장고에 넣으세요.', 'To avoid spoiling, put it in the refridgerator.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2121, '지각하지 안도록 알람을 맞추세요.', 'To not be late, set an alarm.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2122, '먼지가 많이 끼지 않도록 자주 청소하세요.', 'To avoid a lot of dust, clean often.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2123, '잃어버리지 않도록 잘 보이는 곳에 놓으세요.', 'To not lose it, put it in a well visible place.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch13'),
(2124, '하도 추워서 못 했어요.', 'It was so cold I couldn''t do it.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2125, '하도 피곤했어서 늦게 일어났어요.', 'I was so tired I woke up late.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2126, '일이 하도 많아서 못 갔다 왔어요.', 'I had so much work I couldn''t go.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2127, '옷을 많이 하도 입어서 춥지 않아요.', 'I wear so much clothes I don''t feel cold.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2128, '점심을 많이 하도 먹어서 배불라요.', 'I ate so much at lunch I''m full.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2129, '어제 신었던 구두요.', 'The shoes I wore yesterday.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2130, '어제 만들었던 음식요.', 'The food I made yesterday.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2131, '아침에 들었던 음악요.', 'The music I listened to in the morning.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2132, '아까 만셨던 주스요.', 'The juice you made earlier.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2133, '어제 불렀던 노래요.', 'The song you sang yesterday.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2134, '동생도 무서워해요.', 'My younger sibling is scared too.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2135, '아내도 좋아해요.', 'My wife likes it too.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2136, '친구도 힘들어해요.', 'My friend is having a hard time too.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2137, '어머니도 슬퍼하하셨어요.', 'Mother was sad too.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2138, '그 친구도 기뻐했어요.', 'That friend was happy too.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2139, '하면 할수록 재미있어요.', 'The more you do it, the more fun it is.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2140, '만나면 만날수록 마음에 들어요.', 'The more we hang out the more I like him.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2141, '달리기를 하면 할수록 건강해져요.', 'The more you run, the healthier you get.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2142, '들으면 들을수록 좋아요.', 'The more I listen the better it is.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2143, '차가우면 차가울수록 맛있어요.', 'The colder it is, the better it tastes.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch14'),
(2144, '친구에게 집을 알아보게 했어요.', 'I had my friend look for a house.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2145, '친구에게 음식을 준비하게 했어요.', 'I had my friend prepare some food.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2146, '친구에게 비행기 표를 예약하게 했어요.', 'I had my friend book a flight ticket.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2147, '친구에게 고기를 사 오게 했어요.', 'I had my friend buy (and come with) some meat.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2148, '친구에게 집을 청소하게 했어요.', 'I had my friend clean the house.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2149, '부동산에 물어봐야 할걸요.', 'You''re going to have to ask the real estate agent. [I guess]', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2150, '학교 서점에서 팔걸요.', 'They probably sell it at the school bookstore. [I guess]', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2151, '사무실에서 내야 할걸요.', 'You''re gonna have to pay in the office. [I guess]', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2152, '집주인에게 말해야 할걸요.', 'You''ll have to tell the landlord. [I guess]', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2153, '샤오밍 씨가 잘 알걸요.', 'Shoaming would know it well. [I guess]', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2154, '외국어 공부는 메일 하지 않으면 안 돼요.', 'You must study a foreign language every day.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2155, '운동 효과를 보려면 매일 30분 이상 운동 하지 않으면 안 돼요.', 'To see the effect of exercise, you must work out at more than 30 minutes every day.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2156, '여행을 가려면 이번 주까지 여행사에 돈을 입금하지 않으면 안 돼요.', 'If you want to go on the trip you must deposit the money with the travel agency by this week.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2157, '비행기를 타려면 출발 3시간까지 공항에 가지 않으면 안 돼요.', 'To board the plane one must arrive 3 hours early.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2158, '날씨가 아직 쌀쌀해서 긴바지를 입지 않으면 안 돼요.', 'The weather is chilly so one must wear long pants.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2159, '학교 가는 길에 내가 부칠게.', 'I''ll mail it on my way to school.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2160, '밖에 나가는 길에 내가 낼게.', 'On the way out I''ll pay.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2161, '출근하는 길에 내가 버릴게.', 'On my way to work I''ll take out the trash.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2162, '집에 오는 길에 내가 사 올게.', 'I''ll pick it up on the way home. (buy and come with)', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2163, '운동하러 기는 길에 내가 맡길기.', 'I''ll drop it off [at the cleaners] on my way to work out.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch15'),
(2164, '우산만 해요.', 'It''s the size of an umbrella.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2165, '작은 쥐만 해요.', 'It''s the size of a small rat.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2166, '사람만 해요.', 'It''s the size of a person.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2167, '명함만 해요.', 'It''s the size of a business card.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2168, '농구공만 해요.', 'It''s the size of a basketball.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2169, '바빠서 운동할 생각도 못 해요.', 'I''m busy so I can''t even think about exercising.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2170, '비싸서 새 컴퓨터를 살 생각도 못 해요.', 'It''s so expensive I can''t even think about buying a new computer.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2171, '시간이 없어서 김치를 담글 생각도 못해요.', 'I don''t have any time so I can''t even think about making kimchi.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2172, '길이 복잡해서 운전을 할 생각도 못 해요.', 'The roads are so congested I can''t even think about driving.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2173, '일이 많아서 여행 갈 생각도 못 해요.', 'I have too much work to even think about going on a trip.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2174, '정말 먹어 볼 만해요.', 'It''s really worth trying to eat.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2175, '정말 올라가 볼 만해요.', 'It''s really worth trying to go up there (the mountain).', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2176, '정말 가 볼 만해요.', 'It''s really worth trying to go.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2177, '정말 배워 볼 만해요.', 'It''s really worth trying to learn.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2178, '정말 타 볼 만해요.', 'It''s really worth trying to ride.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2179, '단풍이 아름답기로 유명하기거든요.', 'Because it''s famous for beautiful autumn foliage.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2180, '옷이 싸기로 유명하거든요.', 'Because it''s famous for cheap cloths.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2181, '바다가 깨끗하기로 유명하거든요.', 'Because the sea is famous for its clean beaches', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2182, '게가 맛있기로 유명하거든요.', 'Because it''s famous for delicious crab.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2183, '박물관이 많기로 유명하거든요.', 'Because it''s famous for its many museums.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch16'),
(2184, '지하철을 타고 보니 반대 방향으로 가는 열차였어요.', 'After getting on the subway, I realized it was a train going in the opposite direction.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2185, '바지를 사고 보니 너무 작았어요.', 'After buying the pants, I realized they were too small.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2186, '설명을 듣고 보니 이해가 됐어요.', 'After hearing the explanation, I came to understand.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2187, '나중에 알고 보니 대학 동창이었어요.', 'Later, it turned out that they were college classmates.After finding out, I realized he was a college classmate.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2188, '지하철에서 내리고 보니 가방이 없었어요.', 'After getting off the subway, I realized by bag was missing.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2189, '하지만 재미있는 척했어요.', 'But, I pretended it was fun.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2190, '하지만 잘 먹는 척했어요.', 'But, I pretended to [enjoy] the food.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2191, '하지만 알아들은 척했어요.', 'But, I pretended to listen.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2192, '하지만 마음에 드는 척했어요.', 'But, I pretended to like him.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2193, '하지만 모르는 척했어요.', 'But, I pretended not to know.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2194, '네? 시험 문제가 쉽다니요?', 'What?! The test questions are easy?!', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2195, '찌개가 너무 맵다니요?', 'The stew is too spicy?!', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2196, '네? 교실에 아무도 없다니요?', 'What?! There''s no one in the classroom?!', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2197, '일리 씨가 고항에 돌아가다니요?', 'Ali is going back to his hometown?!', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2198, '네? 퇴근하는 길에 교통사고가 나다니요?', 'What?! There was a car accident on the way home from work?!', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2199, '겨울이라고 다 이렇게 추운 건 아니에요.', 'Not all winters are this cold.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2200, '대도시라고 다 공기가 나쁜 건 아니에요.', 'Not all big cities have bad air.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2201, '지하철이라고 다 버스보다 편한 건 아니에요.', 'Not all subways are more comfortable than busses.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2202, '키 큰 사람이라고 다 농구를 잘하는 건 안이에요.', 'Not all tall people are good at basketball.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2203, '이 가게 물건이라고 다 좋은 건 아니에요.', 'Not everything in this store is good.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch17'),
(2204, '제가 봤다니까요.', '[That''s what I just said!] I saw it.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch18'),
(2205, '취소됐다니까요.', '[That''s what I just said!] It''s been canceled.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch18'),
(2206, '100점을 받았다니까요.', '[That''s what I just said!] I got 100 points.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch18'),
(2207, '안 오셨다니까요.', '[That''s what I just said!] He didn''t come.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch18'),
(2208, '결혼반지를 샀다니까요.', '[That''s what I just said!] He bought a wedding ring.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch18'),
(2209, '놓치고 말았어요.', 'I finally ended up missing it after all.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch18'),
(2210, '떨어지고 말았어요.', 'I finally ended up failing after all.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch18'),
(2211, '헤어지고 말았어요.', 'We finally ended up breaking up after all.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch18'),
(2212, '잊어버리고 말았어요.', 'I finally ended up forgetting after all.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch18'),
(2213, '그만두고 말았어요.', 'I finally ended up quitting after all.', 'vocab', '3B', 'SNU SNU.lvl.3 SNU.lvl.3B SNU.lvl.3B.ch18'),
